Subject: [PATCH 020/518] T4240/dts: use rev1.0 sata compatible

To track erratum A-005636 which will be fixed in rev2.0.

Signed-off-by: Shaohui Xie <Shaohui.Xie@freescale.com>
Signed-off-by: Andy Fleming <afleming@freescale.com>
[Grabbed from the branch, LINUX_IR5.2.0, of
https://git.freescale.com/git-private/cgit.cgi/ppc/alu-b4860/linux.git.]
Signed-off-by: Tiejun Chen <tiejun.chen@windriver.com>
---
 arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-post.dtsi |    6 ++++++
 1 files changed, 6 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-post.dtsi b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-post.dtsi
index c388334..52c2aa9 100644
--- a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-post.dtsi
+++ b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-post.dtsi
@@ -320,7 +320,13 @@
 			phy_type = "utmi";
 		};
 /include/ "qoriq-sata2-0.dtsi"
+	sata0: sata@220000 {
+		compatible = "fsl,t4240-rev1.0-sata", "fsl,pq-sata-v2";
+	};
 /include/ "qoriq-sata2-1.dtsi"
+	sata1: sata@221000 {
+		compatible = "fsl,t4240-rev1.0-sata", "fsl,pq-sata-v2";
+	};
 /include/ "qoriq-dce-0.dtsi"
 /include/ "qoriq-pme-0.dtsi"
 
